snippet.title: Tunnel Runner (Atari 2600) - Vizzed.com GamePlay
snippet.description:
ZZZAX Plays Tunnel Runner for Atari 2600 Online: http://www.vizzed.com/playonlinegames/game.php?id=4496
Find the key hidden somewhere in the maze in order to unlock the door to the next "Run". On the way you're pursued by deadly Maze Zots! uh-oh..
